              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SIBAR",
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Delta-E-E telescopes.",
                "The scattering events at large angles were measured",
                "using the corresponding pair of detectors. Each pair",
                "included two silicon(delta-E=SIBAR) detectors of",
                " 20*20 mm  size and 1 mm thickness for the registration",
                "of C-13 and one(E-detector) silicon pin-detector of",
                " 20*20 mm size and 1 mm (or 0.5 mm) thickness for the",
                "registration of C-12."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets were self-supporting films of C-12 with",
                "thicknesses of 0.3, 0.5, 0.57 mg/cm**2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " the telescope method-forward angles"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " kinematical coincidence method -large angles."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.Elastic scattering differential cross",
                "sections for the unsymmetrical 13C+12C system were",
                "measured at the C-13 energy of 250 MeV in the angular",
                "interval 15-93 degree(c.m) using the telescope method-",
                "forward angles and kinematical coincidence method-",
                "large angles."
              ]
            }
          ],
